title: Book, "Voyager Pittoresques de France, Vol. I"
description: Volume I of 8 volumes (1787 - 1789) of French Departments.  41 pages of text (title page lacking) and 53 plates of views etc.  Engravings by Masquelier, Duparc, Cochin, Lienard, and other, after designs of Lallemand, Savard, Lespinasse, and others.

tombstone.epitaph: Book, "Voyager Pittoresques de France, Vol. I". 1955-150-3-1/53.
